<h2 id="一、分类" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#一、分类" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 一、分类</h2>
<div class="language-java line-numbers-mode" data-ext="java"><pre v-pre class="language-java"><code><span class="token comment">// 属性：表示人和物具有的属性，可以加very</span>
beautiful<span class="token operator">:</span> very beautiful
<span class="token comment">// 类别：表示事物的类别, 不可以加very</span>
<span class="token class-name">Chinese</span>、empty
<span class="token comment">// 颜色： 浅色和深色</span>
浅色：<span class="token function">light</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>光<span class="token punctuation">)</span>、<span class="token function">pale</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>微弱，苍白<span class="token punctuation">)</span>、<span class="token function">bright</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>明亮<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
深色：<span class="token function">dark</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>黑暗<span class="token punctuation">)</span>、deep（深）
<span class="token comment">// 强调</span>
<span class="token function">absolute</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>绝对<span class="token punctuation">)</span>、utter（彻底）、total（全部）、entire（整个）
<span class="token comment">// -ing和-ed结尾：</span>
某人某事某种情况的特点表示令人感觉boring（无聊）
<span class="token comment">// 复合：</span>
形容词<span class="token operator">+</span>名词<span class="token operator">+</span>ed，形容词<span class="token operator">/</span>副词<span class="token operator">+</span>过去分词、形容词<span class="token operator">/</span>副词<span class="token operator">/</span>名词<span class="token operator">+</span>现在分词、名词<span class="token operator">+</span>形容词
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="二、顺序" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#二、顺序" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 二、顺序</h2>
<div class="language-java line-numbers-mode" data-ext="java"><pre v-pre class="language-java"><code><span class="token comment">// 限定词</span>
a、an、the、my、your、our
<span class="token comment">// 描绘词</span>
beautiful、boring
<span class="token comment">// 大小长短</span>
big、samll、tall、<span class="token keyword">short</span>
<span class="token comment">// 形状重量</span>
sphere（球）、fat、skinny（瘦的）
<span class="token comment">// 状态</span>
cold、wet（湿的）、rich（丰富的）

<span class="token comment">// 新旧</span>
<span class="token keyword">new</span>、old、ancient（古老的）
<span class="token comment">// 颜色</span>
yellow、red、blue
<span class="token comment">// 图案</span>
spotted（斑点的）、flowery（多花的）

<span class="token comment">// 国籍</span>
<span class="token class-name">Chinese</span>、<span class="token class-name">American</span>、<span class="token class-name">Australian</span>
<span class="token comment">//物质</span>
wooden（木制的）、paper（纸）、platinum（白金）
<span class="token comment">// 类别</span>
working、sleeping、classic（经典的）
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>限&gt;描&gt;大&gt;形&gt;状 &gt;  新&gt;颜&gt;图  &gt;  国&gt;物&gt;类（限描大形状   新颜图  国物类）</p>
<div class="language-java line-numbers-mode" data-ext="java"><pre v-pre class="language-java"><code><span class="token class-name">This</span> is a beautiful small wooden table <span class="token comment">// 这是一个漂亮的小木头桌子</span>
<span class="token class-name">This</span> is a beautiful big sphere broken old yellow patterned <span class="token class-name">American</span> cupreous classic sculpture<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token comment">// 这个一个漂亮的大球形坏掉的老旧黄色带花纹的美国铜质古典雕塑</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="三、用法" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#三、用法" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 三、用法</h2>
<div class="language-java line-numbers-mode" data-ext="java"><pre v-pre class="language-java"><code><span class="token comment">// 作定语</span>
<span class="token class-name">The</span> ship is <span class="token function">huge</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>这船好大<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
<span class="token comment">// 作表语</span>
<span class="token class-name">The</span> books are <span class="token function">interesting</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>这些书有意思<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
<span class="token comment">// 作宾补</span>
<span class="token class-name">The</span> music makes me <span class="token function">happy</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>这个音乐让我开心<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
<span class="token comment">// 作状语</span>
<span class="token class-name">I</span> am off duty now<span class="token punctuation">,</span> tired an <span class="token function">sleepy</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>我现在下班，又困又累<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
<span class="token comment">// 一类人（The + 形容词 ， 代表一类人）</span>
<span class="token class-name">The</span> <span class="token function">old</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>老人<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="四、比较级" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#四、比较级" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 四、比较级</h2>
<h3 id="_4-1-规则变化" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_4-1-规则变化" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 4.1 规则变化</h3>
<div class="language-java line-numbers-mode" data-ext="java"><pre v-pre class="language-java"><code><span class="token comment">// 单音节词和少数双音节词。比较级加er 最高级加est</span>
<span class="token function">warm</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>温暖<span class="token punctuation">)</span>  warmer（更温暖） warmest（最温暖）
<span class="token comment">// 元音加上辅音字母结尾，双写辅音字母。比较级加er，最高级加est</span>
<span class="token function">big</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>大<span class="token punctuation">)</span>  bigger（更大） biggest（最大）
<span class="token comment">// e结尾。比较级加r，最高级加st</span>
large larger largest
<span class="token comment">// y结尾，变y为i。比较级加er，最高级加est</span>
happy happier happiest
<span class="token comment">// 多音节词 单数前面比较级加more，最高级加most</span>
fantastic <span class="token operator">></span> more fantastic <span class="token operator">></span> most fantastic
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h3 id="_4-2-不规则变化" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_4-2-不规则变化" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 4.2 不规则变化</h3>
<p><img src="https://gaoqisen.github.io/GraphBed/202312/20231216225317.png" alt=""></p>
<h3 id="_4-3-用法" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_4-3-用法" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 4.3 用法</h3>
<div class="language-java line-numbers-mode" data-ext="java"><pre v-pre class="language-java"><code><span class="token comment">// 原级：没有比较的意思 或 原级比较表示和什么一样（as...as / the same as / the identical with）</span>
<span class="token class-name">That</span> is <span class="token function">good</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>那很好<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
<span class="token comment">// 比较级：能单独使用，前面能加修饰词（a lot, much, rather, a little, even等），与than连用比较两者</span>
<span class="token class-name">You</span> should be more <span class="token function">patient</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>你应该跟耐心<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
<span class="token class-name">I</span> swim faster than <span class="token function">you</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>我游的比你快<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
<span class="token comment">// 最高级：前面要加the，能单独使用，前面能加修饰词（far,mostly, very, much等）,at + 最高级表示处于最什么状态</span>
<span class="token class-name">That</span> is the best chiose（那个最好的选择）
<span class="token class-name">The</span> car power will at it <span class="token function">best</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>这车的动力将达到最佳状态<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h3 id="_4-4-特殊结构" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_4-4-特殊结构" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 4.4 特殊结构</h3>
<div class="language-java line-numbers-mode" data-ext="java"><pre v-pre class="language-java"><code><span class="token comment">// 比较级and比较级：表示越来越</span>
faster and <span class="token function">faster</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>越来越快<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
<span class="token comment">// 多音节单词：单词可以只写一个，放在最后面</span>
more and more <span class="token function">fantastic</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>越来越了不起<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
<span class="token comment">// the比较级...the比较级： 越怎么越怎么</span>
<span class="token class-name">The</span> richer<span class="token punctuation">,</span> the more <span class="token function">badass</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>越有钱越无法无天<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
<span class="token comment">// more than + 名词 = not only(不仅，不知)</span>
we are more than <span class="token function">friend</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>我们不只是朋友<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
<span class="token comment">// more than + 数词 = very（非常）</span>
<span class="token class-name">We</span> are more than interested in search <span class="token function">gold</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>我们对搜索黄金非常感兴趣<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
<span class="token comment">// more ... than: 第一重意思是比什么多，第二重意思是与其什么不如</span>
<span class="token class-name">My</span> video is more interesting than your <span class="token function">video</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>我的视频比你的视频有趣多了<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
<span class="token class-name">You</span> are more give up than <span class="token function">painful</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>你与其痛苦不如放弃<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
<span class="token comment">// no more than: 只有，仅仅（等于的意思）</span>
<span class="token class-name">I</span> have no more than four <span class="token function">games</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>我只有四款游戏<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
<span class="token comment">// less than: 少于</span>
<span class="token class-name">We</span> leave in less than a <span class="token function">week</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>我们不到一周就走<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
<span class="token comment">// no less than: 多达</span>
<span class="token class-name">The</span> total amount no less than <span class="token number">5000</span> <span class="token function">dollars</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>总金额多达<span class="token number">5</span>千美元<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
<span class="token comment">// not less than: 不少于</span>
<span class="token class-name">I</span> have not less than four <span class="token function">games</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>我有不少于四款游戏<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
<span class="token comment">// no less ... than： 和什么一样</span>
<span class="token class-name">I</span> am no less careful than <span class="token function">you</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>我和你一样小心<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h3 id="_4-5-易混" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_4-5-易混" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 4.5 易混</h3>
<div class="language-java line-numbers-mode" data-ext="java"><pre v-pre class="language-java"><code><span class="token comment">// too much（表太多，修饰名词表数量）, much too（表过分，修饰形容词或副词）</span>
<span class="token class-name">I</span> have too much <span class="token function">money</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>我有太多钱了<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
<span class="token class-name">That</span> is much too <span class="token function">expensive</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>这贵的过分了<span class="token punctuation">)</span>

<span class="token comment">// good（用在定语或者表语）、well（用在状语）</span>
<span class="token class-name">It</span> is good 表语<span class="token punctuation">(</span>他很好<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
<span class="token class-name">Study</span> well and improve every day状语<span class="token punctuation">(</span>好好学习天天向上<span class="token punctuation">)</span>

<span class="token comment">// nice（愉快，指外表）, fine（身体好，天气好）</span>
nice <span class="token function">kill</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>好击杀<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
<span class="token class-name">I</span> am <span class="token function">fine</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>我没事<span class="token punctuation">)</span>

<span class="token comment">// lonely(孤独的，真的孤独), alone（独自，不一定孤独）</span>
<span class="token class-name">The</span> lonely student is starving <span class="token keyword">for</span> <span class="token function">friendship</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>那个孤独的学生渴望友情<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
<span class="token class-name">I</span> live <span class="token function">alone</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>我一个人住<span class="token punctuation">)</span>

<span class="token comment">// quick（速度快），fast（速度快），soon（时间快）</span>
<span class="token class-name">He</span> is a quick <span class="token function">man</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>他是一个快男<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
come <span class="token function">soon</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>很快到来<span class="token punctuation">)</span>

<span class="token comment">// interesting（令...感兴趣）, interested(对...感兴趣)</span>
<span class="token class-name">The</span> book is very <span class="token function">interesting</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>这些书很有趣<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
<span class="token class-name">They</span> are interested in <span class="token class-name">English</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>他们对英语感兴趣<span class="token punctuation">)</span>

<span class="token comment">// living（活着的，存在的，一摸一样的，强烈的）, alive（活着的人）, live（活着的东西）, lively（活泼的、生动的）</span>
<span class="token class-name">The</span> living polymer is high <span class="token function">technology</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>这高活性聚合物是高科技<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
<span class="token class-name">John</span> is alive <span class="token function">yet</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>约翰还活着<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
<span class="token class-name">A</span> live <span class="token function">album</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>一个现场专辑<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
<span class="token class-name">Her</span> lively <span class="token function">mind</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>他灵活的头脑<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div></div></template>


